programme.title: NFL - Greatest Games
programme.desc: Miami Dolphins v San Diego Chargers. A review of the AFC Championship Game played in 1982, which came to be known as the `epic in Miami'. The Chargers started the first quarter in scintillating form, and raced to a 24-0 lead that appeared to have settled the contest in their favour early on. However, The Dolphins battled back in the second quarter, scoring 17 unanswered points to narrow the margin, and at the end of the fourth quarter the teams were tied at 38-38. Despite the extreme heat and humidity, and with many players suffering the effects of dehydration, it took a further 14 minutes of overtime before San Diego kicked a winning field goal to eventually claim a 41-28 victory, and progress to the Super Bowl.(n)

Trans World Sport, 1652. del
programme.desc: Šport je sredstvo množic, kjer se sprostijo pozitivna energija in dobro počutje. Tudi zaradi tega je Trans World Sport oddaja, ki je letos praznovala že 29 letnico delovanja.

programme.title: Italijanska liga (ž): Casalmaggiore - Busto Arsizio
programme.desc: Italijansko žensko državno prvenstvo v odbojki velja za eno od najstarejših na stari celini, saj so prve državne prvakinje na škornju okronali že leta 1946. V prvenstvu se meri 12 ekip, ki med seboj odločijo o naslovu najboljše ekipe v državi. Naslov brani ekipa iz Conegliana.(c)

programme.title: Portugal liga: Benfica - Braga
programme.desc: Nekoč Primeira Liga, danes Liga NOS je najelitnejše nogometno tekmovanje na Portugalskem. V njej vsako leto sodeluje 18 klubov, vendar le pet je takšnih, ki so jo od leta 1934 (datum ustanovitve) tudi osvojili. programme.desc: Gran Canaria in Žalgiris sta neposredna tekmeca za nastop v končnici, zato bo tokratna zmaga štela dvojno. Domači bodo računali tudi na pomoč iz tribun, gostje pa bodo poskušali v čim večji meri pokvariti rajanje na Kanarskih otokih.(n)

programme.title: KHL: Kunlun Red Star - SKA
programme.desc: S polnim imenom Kontinentalna hokejska liga za ligo NHL velja za drugo najmočnejšo hokejsko tekmovanje na svetu. Prvič so tekmovanje izvedeli leta 2008, večina sodelujočih klubov je iz Rusije, devetnajst, po en klub pa iz Belorusije, Latvije, Finske, Slovaške, Kazahstana in Kitajske. Naslov branijo člani Barsa iz Kazana.(n)

programme.title: 1. SRL: Koper - Gorenje Velenje
programme.desc: Koprčani so po prihodu nekdanjega kapetana Uroša Rapotca zaigrali veliko bolje in močno dvignili rezultatsko krivuljo. Primorci so odločeni tudi proti Gorenju drago prodati svojo kožo, kar napoveduje zanimivo srečanje v Bonifiki.(n)

programme.title: Championship: Norwich City - Nottingham Forest
programme.desc: Championship je drugo najmočnejše ligaško tekmovanje v Angliji. V njem nastopa 24 klubov, ki si v 46. krogih skušajo priigrati dve izmed treh vozovnic, ki neposredno vodijo v Premier ligo. Zadnjega potnika med elito dobimo po »playoffu«, v katerega se uvrstijo moštva uvrščena od 3. do 6. mesta po rednem delu.(n)

programme.title: Premier league: Brighton - Arsenal
programme.desc: Arsenalov izjemen niz neporaženosti se je sicer končal, a topničarji še naprej ostajajo med najbolj vročimi ekipami Premier lige, kar bodo poskušali dokazati tudi na gostovanju pri Brightonu.(n)

programme.title: Evroliga - 15. Round: Khimki - Baskonia
programme.desc: Khimki in Baskonia sta sezono začela s podobnimi željami, a vsaj za zdaj ne eni ne drugi niso na mestih, ki prinašajo nastop v končnici. Rusi bodo tokrat poskušali izkoristiti prednost domačega parketa in priti do pomembne zmage.(n)

programme.title: Premier league: Prediction circle
programme.desc: Oglejte si vse zanimivosti pred novim krogom Premier lige.(n)

programme.title: Premier league: Southampton - West Ham
programme.desc: Premier League je profesionalna nogometna liga v Angliji. V njej nastopa 20 klubov, ki se od avgusta do maja borijo za naslov prvaka. Večina tekem je odigranih ob sobotah in nedeljah popoldan, preostalih nekaj krogov pa med tednom zvečer. Premier League je najbolj gledana nogometna liga na svetu. Aktualni prvaki so nogometaši Manchester Cityja.(n)

programme.title: Evroliga - 15. Round: Darussafaka - Olympiacos
programme.desc: Evroliga je najkvalitetnejše in najbolje organizirano klubsko košarkarsko tekmovanje na stari celini. Obeta se nam nova sezona izjemnih košarkarskih užitkov. Najuspešnejši klub je madridski Real, ki je na čelu z izjemnim Luko Dončićem v minuli sezoni znova stopil na vrh Evrope.(n)

programme.title: Turška liga: Buyukcekmece - Belediyespor
programme.desc: Nadaljuje se turško košarkarsko prvenstvo. Kdo bo boljši na obračunu med ekipama Buyukcekmece in Belediyespor?(n)

programme.title: Premier league: Magazin (Sir Alex Ferguson Special)
programme.desc: Edinstven pogled v zakulisje Premier lige. Vse najzanimivejše zgodbe zbrane na enem mestu.(n)

programme.title: Premier league: Watford - Chelsea
programme.desc: Watford je v zadnjem času izgubil kar nekaj točk, vseeno pa ostaja varen pred spodnjim delom lestvice in lahko povsem neobremenjen dočaka Chelsea. Za Londončane na drugi strani šteje samo zmaga, saj Liverpool in Manchester City na vrhu lestvice ne popuščata.(n)

programme.desc: Arnold Palmer Invitational final-round play from Bay Hill Club & Lodge in Orlando, Fla. Last year, Marc Leishman (11-under-par) became the fourth-straight winner here to prevail by one shot. There has not been a playoff since 1999. (cc).

programme.title: PGA Tour Golf: WGC-Dell Technologies Match Play
programme.desc: World Golf Championships-Dell Technologies Match Play finals and third-place match from Austin CC in Texas. Dustin Johnson edged Spain's Jon Rahm 1-up last year to become the first player with wins in all four WGC events. (cc).

programme.title: PGA Tour Golf: Corales Puntacana Resort & Club Championship
programme.desc: Corales Puntacana Resort & Club Championship final-round play in the Dominican Republic. This former Web.com Tour event has a purse of $3 million. Six holes play along the ocean, with the 18th hole requiring a carry over the cliff-lined Bay of Corales. (cc).

programme.title: PGA Tour Golf: Houston Open
programme.desc: Houston Open final-round play from the Golf Club of Houston in Humble, Texas. Last year, Russell Henley racked up 10 birdies in a final-round 65 to win at 20-under-par, three shots better than Sung Kang. (cc).

programme.title: PGA Tour Golf: RBC Heritage
programme.desc: Final-round play in the RBC Heritage in Hilton Head Island, S.C. (cc).

programme.title: PGA Tour Golf: Valero Texas Open
programme.desc: Valero Texas Open final-round play from TPC San Antonio. Kevin Chappell (12-under-par) broke into the PGA Tour winner's circle for the first time in this event last year, nipping Brooks Koepka by one shot in a Monday finish. (cc).

programme.title: PGA Tour Golf: Zurich Classic of New Orleans
programme.desc: Zurich Classic of New Orleans final-round play from TPC Louisiana in Avondale. Alternate-shot play concludes this two-man team event, won last year by Jonas Blixt and Cameron Smith (27-under-par) after four playoff holes vs. Kevin Kisner and Scott Brown. (cc).

programme.title: PGA Tour Golf: Wells Fargo Championship
programme.desc: Wells Fargo Championship final-round play from Quail Hollow Club in Charlotte, N.C. Last year, Brian Harman became the 12th American winner in this event's 15 years, with Rory McIlroy (2010, 2015) and Vijay Singh (2005) claiming the other wins. (cc).

programme.title: PGA Tour Golf: The Players Championship
programme.desc: The Players Championship final-round play from TPC Sawgrass in Ponte Vedra Beach, Fla. South Korea's Si Woo Kim won this unofficial "fifth major" last year at 10-under-par, and was one of just two top-10 finishers to break 70 in the final round. (cc).

programme.title: PGA Tour Golf: AT&T Byron Nelson
programme.desc: AT&T Byron Nelson final-round play from Trinity Forest GC in Dallas. This new links-style layout (designed by Bill Coore and Ben Crenshaw) is the event's 11th different venue. Features include a double green for holes 3 and 11; and the 630-yard 14th. (cc).

programme.title: PGA Tour Golf: Fort Worth Invitational
programme.desc: Fort Worth Invitational final-round play from Colonial CC in Texas. (cc).

programme.title: PGA Tour Golf: Memorial Tournament
programme.desc: Memorial Tournament final-round play from Muirfield Village GC in Dublin, Ohio. (cc).(n)

programme.title: PGA Tour Golf: FedEx St. Jude Classic
programme.desc: FedEx St. Jude Classic final-round play from TPC Southwind in Memphis. Daniel Berger repeated as champ last year, shooting 10-under-par. This course will switch to hosting a World Golf Championships event beginning in 2019. (cc).(n)

programme.title: PGA Tour Golf: Travelers Championship
programme.desc: Travlers Championship final-round play from TPC River Highlands in Cromwell, Conn. (cc).(n)

programme.title: PGA Tour Golf: Quicken Loans National
programme.desc: Final-round play in the Quicken Loans National from TPC Potomac at Avenel Farm in Potomac, Md. This Tiger Woods-hosted event moves to the Detroit area in 2019. Kyle Stanley (7-under-par) won last year in the second playoff in the event's 11-year history. (cc).(n)

programme.title: PGA Tour Golf: A Military Tribute at The Greenbrier
programme.sub-title: A Military Tribute at The Greenbrier
programme.desc: A Military Tribute at The Greenbrier final-round play from The Old White TPC in White Sulpher Springs, W.Va. Xander Schauffele (14-under-par) won by a shot last year over Robert Streb. Four places in the Open Championship are available to top finishers. (cc).(n)

programme.title: PGA Tour Golf: John Deere Classic
programme.desc: John Deere Classic final-round play from TPC Deere Run in Silvis, Ill. (cc).(n)

programme.title: PGA Tour Golf: Barbasol Championship
programme.desc: Barbasol Championship final-round play from Keene Trace GC in Nicholasville, Ky. At a new venue this year, this fourth-year event is the Tour's first non-major in the state of Kentucky since 1959. (cc).(n)

programme.title: PGA Tour Golf: RBC Canadian Open
programme.desc: RBC Canadian Open final-round play from Glen Abbey GC in Oakville, Ont. Last year, Venezuela's Jhonattan Vegas (21-under-par) beat Charley Hoffman in a playoff to become the first repeat winner of this storied event since Jim Furyk in 2006-07. (cc).(n)

programme.title: PGA Tour Golf: WGC-Bridgestone Invitational
programme.desc: World Golf Championships-Bridgestone Invitational final-round play from Firestone CC in Akron, Ohio. This event bids farewell to Firestone in favor of Memphis next year. Hideki Matsuyama won last year at 16-under-par, five better than Zach Johnson. (cc).(n)

programme.title: PGA Tour Golf: Barracuda Championship
programme.desc: Barracuda Championship final-round play from Montreaux Golf and CC in Reno, Nev. Texan Chris Stroud lassoed his maiden Tour win here last year with 44 points in Modified Stableford scoring, outlasting Greg Owen and Richy Werenski in a playoff. (cc).(n)
